name: Bakso Super & Mie Ayam Khas Solo" TIGA PUTRI Mas Yono " GROUP.
address: F62Q+FPV, Jl. Raya Mambal, Mekar Bhuwana, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1:
Little eatery on the side of the road.
We ordered bakso ayam with egg and was super good. It is a chicken broth soup with meatballs and ramen. The super big meatball is stuffed with spices, veggies and chicken meat.
It was super good, I recommend for tourists.
review 2: Really good.. definitely will be 1 of the best delicious bakso in my list .. love the chicken stock taste
